                        "displayName": "Joris Van den Bossche",
                        "active": true,
                        "timeZone": "Europe/Brussels"
                    },
                    "body": "But if we want to be pedantic, then the version bump commit should be the first commit after the branching point ;-) \r\n\r\n(so I would personally not be too pedantic and tie the tag to the version bump commit, which seems most logical to me, and just try to do it not too far after the branching point)",
